node.text:
Hey guys,

Here is my race recap from the weekend.
Guys I am always going to say what’s on my mind and tell it how it is. I might not always be right and I’ll be the first to admit it but I’ll never hold back on how I feel and you will guys will always get the truth from me. No hiding in group chats half truths or dms.
Thanks for all the support and messages I am giving it my everything during the week and on the weekend 

See you all at pala.

node.text:
Hey guys! Who wants to win my Championship 250 replica CRF 110? 🤯
.
As you guys know I won the outdoors championship this past weekend so I partnered up with the guys over at @motorsportscurated to hook one of you UP with a free 110 to be rolling around just like me!
.
RULES TO ENTER :
✅ FOLLOW EVERYONE @MOTORSPORTSCURATED FOLLOWS
✅ TAG UNLIMITED FRIENDS
.
Winner will be selected September 26th ( Worldwide entries accepted ) If you are close to where I’m at I might just deliver this bike personally to YOU!
